{"data":[{"id":563805902,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":307595822,"title":"高中生对哥德巴赫猜想的证明有哪些错误？","question_type":"normal","created":1546272354,"updated_time":1546301579,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"aafd14084b445ea89aed6836b8e10ee1","url_token":"zhang-guo-yu","name":"张国钰","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/c737aee3b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/c737aee3b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/aafd14084b445ea89aed6836b8e10ee1","user_type":"people","headline":"技术各来一点的小白","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":559,"is_followed":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563805902","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546280353,"updated_time":1546280353,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":4,"comment_count":0,"is_sticky":false,"admin_closed_comment":false,"comment_permission":"all","can_comment":{"reason":"","status":true},"reshipment_settings":"allowed","content":"\u003cp\u003e大家都这么认真么？还截图分析指出错误。想想都不可能啊，全世界的数学家又不是吃素的，如果一个高中生真能解开，别说数学家脸疼，我觉得数学体系都要崩塌吧。就当做辞旧迎新的段子，吃瓜凑个热闹就好嘞。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我觉得吧，对于一个高中生，可能还是青春期吧，有点懵懂无知，虽然我是个学渣，不好在学习相关的说太多，但我想，大家与其在他的错误中取乐或者批评，不如好好给他一些正面的指导，毕竟他还有很长的路，还有很多可能性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e而我想说的是， \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e 不管你是不是真的天才，对学术，对这个世界，对你身边的人，学会保持一颗敬畏之心很重要。很多东西，它如果能成为丰碑一样的存在，就绝不可能那么简单就能属于你的，即使你有可能，至少也要经历一定的历练，到了一定高度，以及知识，经验，能力的沉淀后，才能配得上它。还有就是，这个世界充满了各种猜想，可能会比解开哥德巴赫猜想给你带来的价值更有实际意义，是值得你去专研和摸索的，千万别过于的砖牛角尖，耽误了自己的前程。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e祝好，新年快乐。\u003c/p\u003e","editable_content":"","excerpt":"大家都这么认真么？还截图分析指出错误。想想都不可能啊，全世界的数学家又不是吃素的，如果一个高中生真能解开，别说数学家脸疼，我觉得数学体系都要崩塌吧。就当做辞旧迎新的段子，吃瓜凑个热闹就好嘞。我觉得吧，对于一个高中生，可能还是青春期吧，有点…","collapsed_by":"nobody","collapse_reason":"","annotation_action":[],"mark_infos":[],"relevant_info":{"is_relevant":false,"relevant_type":"","relevant_text":""},"suggest_edit":{"reason":"","status":false,"tip":"","title":"","unnormal_details":{"status":"","description":"","reason":"","reason_id":0,"note":""},"url":""},"is_labeled":false,"reward_info":{"can_open_reward":false,"is_rewardable":false,"reward_member_count":0,"reward_total_money":0,"tagline":""},"relationship":{"is_author":false,"is_authorized":false,"is_nothelp":false,"is_thanked":false,"voting":0,"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.follower_count%2Cbadge%5B%2A%5D.topics\u0026limit=1\u0026offset=138\u0026platform=desktop\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/307595822/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cadmin_closed_comment%2Creward_info%2Cis_collapsed%2Cannotation_action%2Cannotation_detail%2Ccollapse_reason%2Cis_sticky%2Ccollapsed_by%2Csuggest_edit%2Ccomment_count%2Ccan_comment%2Ccontent%2Ceditable_content%2Cvoteup_count%2Creshipment_settings%2Ccomment_permission%2Ccreated_time%2Cupdated_time%2Creview_info%2Crelevant_info%2Cquestion%2Cexcerpt%2Crelationship.is_authorized%2Cis_author%2Cvoting%2Cis_thanked%2Cis_nothelp%2Cis_labeled%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.mark_infos%5B%2A%5D.url%3Bdata%5B%2A%5D.author.fol